WEBVTT

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:35.696
is the ability to make people's dreams
of being someone else a reality.

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.296
That's like a drug

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:39.496
which pushes me to keep working,

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:41.480
even without metrics.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:45.016
One of my models

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:49.296
had always dreamed
of being seen as a warrior,

00:04:49.320 --> 00:04:53.360
but she wasn't able to do sports
because of her health problems.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.296
Half a year ago, she passed away

00:04:56.320 --> 00:04:59.480
from heart disease at the age of 22.